e  decrease in the public debt for those years.  But he paid down the  public debt by borrowing far <em>more</em> money in the form of intragovernmental holdings (mostly Social Security).</blockquote>', 'The Myth of the Clinton Surplus', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '242-revision-4', '', '', '2011-04-16 14:18:49', '2011-04-16 14:18:49', '', 242, 'http://ttmsoia.andyhill.us/2011/04/16/242-revision-4/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
