(444, 1, '2011-07-04 23:17:52', '2011-07-04 23:17:52', 'This site is brilliant satire. Written from the perspective of MOTUS (Mirror of the United States), it follows the daily actions of the first couple and the administration, with other current events thrown in. An example of the brilliance: MOTUS was designed by NASA (funding reduction and change of mission under Obama) and gets its warranty (health care) through them. Extremely snarky, but also informative of the day to day happenings of the administration (lots of links to <a href=\"http://whitehouse.gov\" target=\"_blank\">http://whitehouse.gov</a>).\r\n\r\nGreat post (prove me wrong):\r\nhttp://www.michellesmirror.com/2011/07/feelin-pretty-damned-unappreciated.html\r\n\r\nSo, yeah, <a href=\"http://www.michellesmirror.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Michelle\'s Mirror</a> rules the school.\r\n\r\nhttp://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A2Rab9aKkXk&amp;feature=player_embedded', 'Michelle Obama\'s Mirror', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'michelle-obamas-mirror', '', '', '2011-07-04 23:17:52', '2011-07-04 23:17:52', '', 0, 'http://ttmsoia.andyhill.us/?p=444', 0, 'post', '', 2),
