p://openstates.org/\" target=\"_blank\">openstates.org</a> are products of the <a href=\"http://sunlightfoundation.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Sunlight Foundation </a>which is where I get most of my current data, via their <a href=\"http://sunlightfoundation.com/api/\" target=\"_blank\">APIs</a>.', 'InformedElectorate.net', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '766-revision', '', '', '2014-01-12 00:23:21', '2014-01-12 00:23:21', '', 766, 'http://ttmsoia.andyhill.us/2014/01/12/766-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
