ute hell in\r\na million years: in fact, if Christianity is true, Hell is the precisely correct technical term for what it\r\nwould be. And immortality makes this other difference, which, by the by, has a connection with the\r\ndifference between totalitarianism and democracy.', 'On the Nature of Hell (Assuming There Is One)', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '916-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-26 18:20:10', '2014-04-26 23:20:10', '', 916, 'http://ttmsoia.andyhill.us/2014/04/26/916-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
